HEADWORD: Detur
<hw>De"tur</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>detur</ets> let it be given.]</ety> <def>A present of books given
to a meritorious undergraduate student as a prize.</def> <mark>[Harvard
Univ., U. S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

